	The package name under Debian-based system is geoip.

	Add additional IPs from the MaxMind GeoIP database:

	$ wget http://geolite.maxmind.com/download/geoip/database/GeoLiteCountry/GeoIP.dat.gz
	$ wget http://geolite.maxmind.com/download/geoip/database/GeoLiteCity.dat.gz
	$ wget http://download.maxmind.com/download/geoip/database/asnum/GeoIPASNum.dat.gz
	$ gunzip GeoIP.dat.gz
	$ gunzip GeoIPASNum.dat.gz
	$ gunzip GeoLiteCity.dat.gz
	$ sudo cp GeoIP.dat GeoIPASNum.dat GeoLiteCity.dat /usr/share/GeoIP/ 

	We can also use curl and the following URL:

	curl ipinfo.io/23.66.166.151

