youtube-dl

	youtube-dl --audio-format mp4 --audio-quality 0 --recode-video mkv $URL
	--recode-video - decode in format
	--audio-quality - default is 5; 0 is better, 9 is worse
	--audio-format - specify audio format
	
	Get available formats and quality:
	youtube-dl -F $URL
	Then, a specific format can be downloaded with the format code in the right column:
	youtube-dl -f 22 $URL

	Specify one option for the video and one for the audio (the video format code comes first):
	youtube-dl -f 135+140 $URL

