OSI (to do):

Application Layer - HTTP, IMAP, LDAP, NNTP, POP, DNS, IRC, XMPP and so forth
Presentation Layer
Session Layer
Transport Layer - TCP, UDP
Network Layer - Authentication, TCP/IP, IPX
Internet Layer - IPv4, IPv6
